title: 1966 United States Senate election in Texas
text: The 1966 United States Senate election in Texas was held on November 8, 1966. Incumbent <a href="Republican%20Party%20%28United%20States%29">Republican</a> U.S. Senator <a href="John%20Tower">John Tower</a> was re-elected to a second term in office over Democratic <a href="Attorney%20General%20of%20Texas">Attorney General of Texas</a> <a href="Waggoner%20Carr">Waggoner Carr</a>.
